data.description: Located in one of SD County's top suburbs, this home is positioned on a sizable terraced lot & features wood floors, a large family room & a modern kitchen w/white quartz island/counters & newer SS appliances. The recently renovated primary bath feels like you're at the spa! Relax & entertain in the backyard/deck area. Added perks include PAID OFF 12 PANEL SOLAR, mini-split zoned heating/air & tankless water heater. Minutes to downtown La Mesa. Near freeways, shopping, dining, schools & more!Home improvements include: Paid off solar, added full bath w/ dual sinks & anti-fog LED dimmable lighted mirrors & pocket door, new GE ventless wash/dryer, new stove 2023, new Samsung Bespoke refrigerator w/ changeable clementine and sunrise yellow glass panels 2023, new dishwasher 2022, new windows to back room 2022, new back door, new garage window, new mini split 2019, new tankless water heater 2020.  One bedroom has been converted into office/ laundry, with built in floor-to-ceiling cabinets, desk & laundry hookups added to room, which can easily be converted back.
